<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 01:52:40 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>比特币内部 2026：忠实者超越价格的一年</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-04-30/inside-bitcoin-2026-the-year-the-faithful-outgrew-the-price</link><description>比特币品牌的销售已经超越了图表。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iEYAiZlK4sDw/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-04-30/inside-bitcoin-2026-the-year-the-faithful-outgrew-the-price</guid></item><item><title>拉斯维加斯比特币的大力支持者努力策划反弹</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-30/bitcoin-faithful-came-to-las-vegas-but-the-price-didn-t-show-up</link><description>每年有那么几天，世界上最狂热的比特币信徒会戴着橙色牛仔帽、系着领带、穿着 T 恤聚集在一起，高呼价值 100 万美元的比特币。今年，在拉斯维加斯，这些口号对每个人都有效——除了市场。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iYXzZtn8oNlc/v2/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 17:56:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-30/bitcoin-faithful-came-to-las-vegas-but-the-price-didn-t-show-up</guid></item><item><title>埃里克·特朗普 (Eric Trump) 从陷入困境的金融科技公共领导层中消失</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-30/eric-trump-disappears-from-troubled-fintech-s-public-leadership</link><description>埃里克·特朗普(Eric Trump)已从拉斯维加斯一家小型公司的公共领导层中消失，这家公司与其家族的加密货币公司世界自由金融公司(World Liberty Financial Inc.)关系密切。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ii_JhJD6Ab_8/v2/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 11:46:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-30/eric-trump-disappears-from-troubled-fintech-s-public-leadership</guid></item><item><title>Tether 敦促 Jack Mallers 的“二十一”进行罢工和矿工交易</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-30/tether-proposes-mergers-involving-bitcoin-treasury-company</link><description>Tether 提议 Twenty One Capital 与加密货币交易和支出平台 Strike 以及比特币挖矿公司 Elektron Energy 合并，而此时 Twenty One Capital 投资比特币的主要业务已经失宠。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/itQPSikuECwc/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:47:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-30/tether-proposes-mergers-involving-bitcoin-treasury-company</guid></item><item><title>期权交易者以 80,000 美元围绕比特币搭建“电子围栏”</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-29/option-traders-build-electric-fence-around-bitcoin-at-80-000</link><description>比特币一直逼近8万美元，但仍难以突破。原因之一：期权市场中的一股隐藏力量正在对其产生不利影响。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ioEL9BrYJSPg/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 15:53:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-29/option-traders-build-electric-fence-around-bitcoin-at-80-000</guid></item><item><title>捷克央行行长表示比特币可能有助于增加储备</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-28/czech-central-banker-says-bitcoin-may-improve-reserve-portfolio</link><description>捷克共和国最高央行行长 Ales Michl 周二表示，将比特币添加到该银行的官方储备中可以改善投资组合的表现，最新评论表明该机构继续认真考虑多元化发展数字资产。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ik3kfo_1G8no/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 20:10:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-28/czech-central-banker-says-bitcoin-may-improve-reserve-portfolio</guid></item><item><title>加密货币公司 MoonPay 押注 1 亿美元用于机构推动</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-29/crypto-firm-moonpay-bets-100-million-for-institutional-push</link><description>MoonPay Inc. 收购了以色列加密安全初创公司 Sodot，这是该加密支付公司计划推出一个专门致力于满足机构对数字资产需求的新部门的一部分。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ihaRJeExzYiA/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-29/crypto-firm-moonpay-bets-100-million-for-institutional-push</guid></item><item><title>稳定币巨头 Tether 领投阿根廷加密货币应用程序</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-29/stablecoin-giant-tether-leads-investment-in-argentine-crypto-app</link><description>Tether 通过投资阿根廷加密平台 Belo 进一步进军拉丁美洲。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQwyGymKEOJM/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-29/stablecoin-giant-tether-leads-investment-in-argentine-crypto-app</guid></item></channel></rss>